OL,3,CTottenham confirm appointment of
OL,4,CRoberto De Zerbi as new boss on five-
OL,5,Cyear deal
OL,7,FRoberto De Zerbi has been confirmed as
OL,8,FTottenham's new head coach on a five-
OL,9,Fyear deal, but no relegation release
OL,10,Fclause has been included in his
OL,11,Fcontract.
OL,13,FSpurs parted company with Igor Tudor
OL,14,Fon Sunday afternoon after five defeats
OL,15,Fin seven matches during a shambolic 44-
OL,16,Fday reign and immediately set their
OL,17,Fsights on trying to lure number one
OL,18,Fsummer target De Zerbi to join mid-
OL,19,Fseason.
