PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775139065
OL,3,CTottenham confirm appointment of
OL,4,CRoberto De Zerbi as new boss on five-
OL,5,Cyear deal
OL,7,FAfter days of negotiations given De
OL,8,FZerbi's initial preference to assess
OL,9,Fhis options in the summer, the 46-year-
OL,10,Fold accepted Tottenham's proposal and
OL,11,Fdespite relegation being a realistic
OL,12,Fprospect with seven matches of a
OL,13,Fterrible Premier League campaign left,
OL,14,Fthe Press Association understands no
OL,15,Frelegation clause has been included.
OL,17,FDe Zerbi said: "I am delighted to be
OL,18,Fjoining this fantastic football club,
OL,19,Fwhich is one of the biggest and most
OL,20,Fprestigious in the world.
OL,26,@yD@POU
