CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775139065
OL,3,CTottenham confirm appointment of
OL,4,CRoberto De Zerbi as new boss on five-
OL,5,Cyear deal
OL,7,F"In all my discussions with the club's
OL,8,Fleadership, their ambition for the
OL,9,Ffuture has been clear ` to build a
OL,10,Fteam capable of reaching great
OL,11,Fachievements, and to do that playing a
OL,12,Fstyle of football that excites and
OL,13,Finspires our supporters. I am here
OL,14,Fbecause I believe in that ambition and
OL,15,Fhave signed a long-term contract to
OL,16,Fgive everything to deliver it.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
