OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1775139065
OL,3,CTottenham confirm appointment of
OL,4,CRoberto De Zerbi as new boss on five-
OL,5,Cyear deal
OL,7,F"Our short-term priority is to climb
OL,8,Fthe Premier League table, which will
OL,9,Fbe the complete focus until the final
OL,10,Fwhistle of the last game of the
OL,11,Fseason. I'm looking forward to getting
OL,12,Fout on the training pitch and working
OL,13,Fwith these players to achieve that."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
